Package: datasailr
Type: Package
Title: DataSailr Makes it Easy to Manipulate Data Row by Row, Using Sailr Lang
Version: 0.8.0
Date: 2020-01-23
Author: Toshihiro Umehara <toshi@niceume.com>
Maintainer: Toshihiro Umehara <toshi@niceume.com>
Authors@R: person("Toshihiro", "Umehara", email="toshi@niceume.com", role=c("aut", "cre"))
Description: DataSailr enables row by row data manipulation. You can write data manipulation code in Sailr lang which is specially intended for the data manipulation. The package uses libsailr (C/C++ library) for its Sailr code parsing and its execution.
License: GPL (>= 3) 
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.12.18)
Suggests: RUnit
LinkingTo: Rcpp
SystemRequirements: GNU make
